Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the Telford & Wrekin unparished. 
    See also Table 2, notes (a, (i)) and (j).

That part which until 21.8.1936 formed part of the parish of 
    Woodcote. 
    See also Table 2, note (d).

Created 1.10.1898 out of the parish of Wellington Rural. See 
    also Table 2, note (j).

Created 1.4.1934 out of the parish of Wrockwardine Wood, Wombridge, 
    Priorslee, St. George's, Hadley, Shifnal and Wellington Rural. Abolished 1.4.1974 
    and added to the Telford & Wrekin unparished area. See also Table 2, notes 
    (b), (c) and (j).

Abolished 1.4.1966 and added to the parish of Dawley. See 
    also Table 2, notes (a) and (j).

Abolished 1894 to become the separate parishes of Wellington Urban 
    and Wellington Rural.

Created 1894 from the rural part of the parish of Wellington. 
    See also Table 2, note (j).

Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Wellington in Wellington 
    Urban District. Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the Telford & Wrekin unparished 
    area. See also Table 2, note (j).
Abolished 1.4.1934 and added to the parish of Oakengates.

Created 25.3.1884 out of the parishes of Eyton upon the Weald 
    Moors, Preston upon the Weald Moors and Wrockwardine. Abolished 1.4.1934 and added to the parish of Oakengates.
